Bradly A. Merlie

Age : 57Public asset : 847,891 USDLinked companies : No connection available 





Summary 



Mr. Bradly A. Merlie is Vice President-Information Services at Piedmont Natural Gas Co., Inc. and Regional Director-Operations at Williams International.He is on the Board of Directors at International House (North carolina) and Apparo Solutions, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from North Carolina State University.



